    <h2 id="pancakes">Fluffy Pancakes</h2>
    <img class="recipe-image" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/50/Pancakes_%28Bakery%29.jpg/800px-Pancakes_%28Bakery%29.jpg" alt="Pancakes">
    
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Time:</strong> 20 minutes</li>
        <li><strong>Serves:</strong> 4 people</li>
    </ul>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Ingredients</th>
                <th>Quantity</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Flour</td>
                <td>1 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Milk</td>
                <td>1 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Eggs</td>
                <td>2</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sugar</td>
                <td>2 tbsp</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Mix all ingredients in a bowl until smooth.</p>
    <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Heat a pan and pour the batter to make pancakes.</p>
    <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Cook until golden brown, flip, and cook the other side.</p>

    <p><em>Source: <a href="https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/21014/good-old-fashioned-pancakes/">AllRecipes</a></em></p>

